import argparse

def main(project, runner, staging_location, temp_location, num_workers, worker_machine_type, setup_file, region, storage_bucket):
    command = f'{project}     --runner {runner}     --staging_location gs://{storage_bucket}/{staging_location}     --temp_location gs://{storage_bucket}/{temp_location}     --num_workers {num_workers}     --worker_machine_type {worker_machine_type}     --setup_file {setup_file}     --region {region}     --storage-bucket {storage_bucket}     '
    return command
